=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::GestureRotate
=head1 Description

B<Gnome::Gtk4::GestureRotate> is a L<Gnome::Gtk4::Gesture|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Gesture> for 2-finger rotations.

Whenever the angle between both handled sequences changes, the
I<angle-changed> signal is emitted.

